        Constructs a new instance of this extractor, which extracts commits from SVN repositories on any platform.
        Parameters:
        extractionProperties - the properties of the properties file defining the extraction process and the configuration of the extractor in use; all properties, which start with the prefix "extraction."
        commitQueue - the IExtractionQueue for transferring commits from an extractor to an analyzer
